@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nsyhst(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.16
    v1 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.40) + (v2 + 0.58 * v0 + 0.04)) / 0.47)
    v1 = (wp.cos(v1) * (wp.sin(v0 + 0.45) + wp.abs(v0 + 0.91)))
    tmp = ((tmp * 0.34) + ((v1 + 0.58 * v0 + 0.33) * (v2 + 0.19 / tmp + 0.77)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.exp((tmp + 0.86 + tmp + 0.72)))
    data[tid] = v0
